gion including credit cards and consumer banking institutional banking wealth management and alternative investments he is also a member of the company’s senior leadership and executive committees at mastercard banga  will be responsible for key business operations including customer relationships globally in international and us markets products services marketing technology and operations the companys finance human resources and law and franchise integrity functions will continue to report to selander i am very pleased to have ajay join our senior executive team and partner with me to grow mastercards value to our customers merchants consumers and investors said selander ajays experience in diverse industries and diverse geographies will reinforce and strengthen our global competencies as electronic payments continue to accelerate worldwide with his expertise and leadership selander said we hope to capture even more of the significant global payments opportunity this is clearly a wonderful opportunity to join a company at the forefront of advancing global commerce said banga from its strong technology base to its local market expertise mastercard has many important resources in place to make life easier for consumers and payment systems more efficient for businesses and governments around the world i look forward to joining my new colleagues and continuing the success they have so well architected over the years banga stated banga who joined citi in  as head of marketing and sales in india quickly rose through the ranks to head of sales marketing and business development for europe middle east and africa based in brussels and was then appointed division executive consumer bank for central and eastern europe middle east and africa based in london in  he was appointed business head citifinancial and us consumer assets and in  became executive vice president global consumer group and president retail banking north america he was named chairman and chief executive officer of citi’s global consumer group international in  which included all credit card and consumer banking operations outside north america he was appointed to his current position in  prior to joining citigroup he spent  years with nestle india and two years with pepsico banga serves on the board of directors of kraft foods inc he is also on the board of trustees of the asia society has served as vice chairman of the board of trustees of the new york hall of science and was a board member of the national urban league he graduated with a ba in economics honors from delhi university and is also a graduate of the indian institute of management ahmedabad about mastercard incorporated mastercard incorporated advances global commerce by providing a critical economic link among financial institutions businesses cardholders and merchants worldwide as a franchisor processor and advisor mastercard develops and markets payment solutions processes approximately  billion transactions each year and provides industryleading analysis and consulting services to financialinstitution customers and merchants powered by the mastercard worldwide network and through its family of brands including mastercard® maestro® and cirrus® mastercard serves consumers and businesses in more than  countries and territories for more information go to wwwmastercardcom back to top      mastercard all rights reserved ajaypal singh banga  wikipedia ajaypal singh banga from wikipedia the free encyclopedia jump to navigation search ajaypal singh banga born  pune india residence purchase new york us nationality indian alma mater iim ahmedabad mba delhi university ba occupation ceo and president mastercard predecessor robert selander ajaypal ajay singh banga is the current president and chief executive officer of mastercard mastercard announced on april   that ajay banga previously mastercard’s president and chief operating officer had been named by the board of directors to serve as the company’s president and chief executive officer effective july   the company also announced that banga would become a member of mastercard’s board of directors effective immediately banga  succeeded robert w selander who had been mastercard’s chief executive officer since march  on thursday february   president barack obama appointed banga to serve as a member of the presidents advisory committee for trade policy and negotiations presently he is also the chairman of the usindia business council usibc representing more than three hundred of the largest international companies investing in india he is also a member of board of directors of the dow chemical company member of the council on foreign relations and member of international business council of the world economic forum the government of india awarded him the civilian honour of the padma shri in  contents  early life  education  career  see also  references  external links early lifeedit born into a sikh family in khadki pune maharashtra in india where his father an army officer was posted the familys origin is from jalandhar in punjab his father is retired lieutenantgeneral harbhajan singh banga who is a decorated army general of indian army he is also the younger brother of another wellknown ceo m s banga banga grew up and schooled across india successively in secunderabad jalandhar delhi hyderabad and in shimla where he finished his schooling educationedit banga went on to graduate with a bachelor of arts honours degree in economics from st stephens college delhi university and mba from the indian institute of management ahmedabad  careeredit beginning his business career with nestlé in  banga spent the next  years working in jobs spanning sales marketing and general management he later joined pepsico and was involved in the launch of its international fast food franchises in india as the economy liberalized banga was vice chairman of the board of trustees of the new york hall of science and a board member of the national urban league he was formerly a business sponsor of citis african heritage network – nyc banga has a keen interest in social development issues and over the period from  to mid he spearheaded citis strategy in the microfinance sector across the world banga is a regular speaker at various fintech conferences and various leadership conferences he also appeared on the mad money show hosted by jim cramer on thursday  nov  banga was the keynote speaker at the nyu stern  graduate convocation on may   where he spoke about the importance of diversity in driving innovation and leadership he also was a keynote speaker for his alma mater the indian institute of management ahmedabad during the class of s convocation see alsoedit indians in the new york city metropolitan region referencesedit  a b reshmanth april   these ceos of indian origin will make you feel proud south report retrieved may     httpwwwmastercardcomuscompanyennewsroomceotransitionannouncementhtml  httpwwwmastercardcomuscompanyennewsroomceotransitionannouncementhtml  httpwwwwhitehousegovthepressofficepresidentobamaannouncesmorekeyadministrationposts  httpwwwlatestgktodaycomajaypalsinghbangaappointedasmemberofusadvisorycommitteefortradepolicyandnegotiations  padma awards  press information bureau government of india  retrieved february     httptimesofindiaindiatimescombizinternationalbusinessdelhiwhizajaybangabecomesmastercardceoarticleshowcms  temporary primary source  httpexpressbuzzcomtopiciimalumnusajaybangaisnewceoofmastercardhtml  httpwwwmastercardcomuscompanyennewsroomceotransitionannouncementhtml  httpwwwcnbccomid  httpwwwsternnyueduexperiencesternnewseventsbangakeynoteconvocation  httpsqzcomajaybangassixlessonsonleadershipastoldtotheiimaclassof external linksedit appearances on cspan retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitleajaypalsinghbangaoldid categories american chief executives of financial services companiesbusinesspeople from puneliving peopleindian institute of management ahmedabad alumniameric