ass of s convocation see alsoedit indians in the new york city metropolitan region referencesedit  a b reshmanth april   these ceos of indian origin will make you feel proud south report retrieved may     httpwwwmastercardcomuscompanyennewsroomceotransitionannouncementhtml  httpwwwmastercardcomuscompanyennewsroomceotransitionannouncementhtml  httpwwwwhitehousegovthepressofficepresidentobamaannouncesmorekeyadministrationposts  httpwwwlatestgktodaycomajaypalsinghbangaappointedasmemberofusadvisorycommitteefortradepolicyandnegotiations  padma awards  press information bureau government of india  retrieved february     httptimesofindiaindiatimescombizinternationalbusinessdelhiwhizajaybangabecomesmastercardceoarticleshowcms  temporary primary source  httpexpressbuzzcomtopiciimalumnusajaybangaisnewceoofmastercardhtml  httpwwwmastercardcomuscompanyennewsroomceotransitionannouncementhtml  httpwwwcnbccomid  httpwwwsternnyueduexperiencesternnewseventsbangakeynoteconvocation  httpsqzcomajaybangassixlessonsonleadershipastoldtotheiimaclassof external linksedit appearances on cspan retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitleajaypalsinghbangaoldid categories american chief executives of financial services companiesbusinesspeople from puneliving peopleindian institute of management ahmedabad alumniamerican people of indian punjabi descentamerican sikhsindian emigrants to the united statesamerican chief operating officersrecipients of the padma shri in trade and industry birthshidden categories articles with hcards navigation menu personal tools not logged intalkcontributionscreate accountlog in namespaces article talk variants views read edit view history more search navigation main pagecontentsfeatured contentcurrent eventsrandom articledonate to wikipediawikipedia store interaction helpabout wikipediacommunity portalrecent changescontact page tools what links hererelated changesupload filespecial pagespermanent linkpage informationwikidata itemcite this page printexport creat